<li><a href="http://csicop.org/si/2001-03/stare.html" class="external text" title="http://csicop.org/si/2001-03/stare.html" rel="nofollow">Sheldrake's response</a> to the <a href="/wiki/CSICOP" title="CSICOP" class="mw-redirect">CSICOP</a> critique</li>
<li><a href="http://www.cbc.ca/ideas/features/science/index.html#episode9" class="external text" title="http://www.cbc.ca/ideas/features/science/index.html#episode9" rel="nofollow">CBC Ideas: How To Think About Science, Episode 9</a></li>
<li><a href="http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=2769779850168739190" class="external text" title="http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=2769779850168739190" rel="nofollow">Rupert Sheldrake</a> at <a href="/wiki/Google_Video" title="Google Video">Google Video</a> – Google Tech Talk September 2, 2008 – <i>The Extended Mind: Recent Experimental Evidence</i></li>
</ul>
<table class="navbox" cellspacing="0" style=";">
